}

<div style="display: flex; text-align: center; flex-direction: column; width: 100%">
    <div style="height: 400px; width: 80%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto">
        <h1>Our Mission</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: gray">
            Our mission is to empower individuals to manage their finances
            effectively through easy expense tracking, budget planning, goal setting,
            detailed reports, and expert advisor consultations. We are committed to making
            financial management simple, accessible, and effective for everyone.
        </p>
